query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag AS t1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('algorithm',
'awk',
'c',
'centos',
'jquery',
'networking',
'oracle',
'permissions',
'programming-challenge',
'security',
'sql-server-2012',
'strings') AND s.site_name IN ('codereview',
'dba',
'magento',
'unix')
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Enthusiast',
'Excavator',
'Guru',
'Promoter') group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
